{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choppy Waters is a quirky, sushi-themed roguelite deckbuilder. Gather fresh ingredients, craft powerful sushi cards, and engage in turn-based tactical battles as you navigate a procedurally generated map. Discover clever synergies to outwit pirates, cultists, and all manner of monstrous foes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2677980/extras/GIF_9-30-2024_4-12-36_PM.gif?t=1733181725\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Test your deck building skills in strategic battles against pirates, cultists, and strange creatures. Cleverly combine ingredients to create powerful synergies as you embark on your journey through Choppy Waters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2677980/extras/GIF_9-30-2024_4-19-55_PM.gif?t=1733181725\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Handpick ingredients to craft sushi with unique abilities, curating powerful collections of cards unique to your playstyle. Uncover hidden synergies between ingredients and sushi cards to outwit the diverse enemies you\u2019ll encounter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2677980/extras/GIF_9-30-2024_4-43-53_PM.gif?t=1733181725\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Upgrade and refine your sushi cards as you grow stronger with each run through Choppy Waters. Seek out rare ingredients and enhance your sushi-making prowess to face the escalating challenges that lie ahead!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2677980/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733181725","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steams